1. *Govorimo* srpski jezik. (We are speaking Serbian language.) 
2. Moja porodica *govori* našem jeziku. (My family speaks our language.)
3. Mi *govorimo* o sadašnjim temama. (We are talking about current topics.) 
4. Oni su *govorili* o svojim planovima. (They were talking about their plans.)
5. Njegova porodica *govorila* o mogućnostima. (His family was talking about the possibilities.) 
6. Ljudi *govore* o tome kako da se izrazimo. (People are talking about how to express ourselves.) 
7. Oni *govore* o tome kako da se povežu. (They are talking about how to connect.) 
8. *Govorimo* o tome da li ćemo uspeti. (We are talking about whether we will succeed.)